{"tid":625142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙拳難敵四手　廟街男遭肥瘦漢狂毆","createTime":"2018-04-11T07:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:50:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3397f1b9490a024e4e2cc61f6eb4cd24030cbb5d","tid":625142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358389?_ga=2.36225056.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358389%3F_ga%3D2.36225056.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=e9b57mX1U%2F8HESOwWlL%2FBY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=53d94f3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358389%3F_ga%3D2.36225056.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=f75f9eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358389?_ga=2.36225056.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n雙拳難敵四手　廟街男遭肥瘦漢狂毆<br />\n<br />\n5.3K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】油麻地廟街63號對開發生襲擊傷人案。昨凌晨零時許，警方接獲報案，指有一批人在街頭打鬥，警員趕至現場，發現一名45歲姓李男子，眼及臉部受傷，且滿身酒氣，他報稱遭兩名男子襲擊毆打，事後由救護員送院治理，警員展開調查及在附近一帶進行兜截。"}]}